    ["69466aaa676cc442cdb01894"] = {
        ["EndTimestamp"] = 1766523599,
        ["Content"] = {
            [1] = {
                ["title"] = "「大风歌·上」版本更新说明",
                ["title1"] = "「大风歌·上」版本更新说明",
                ["language"] = "CN",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_版本维护更新说明.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"GPN2dXtpjoQYpCxt18DcvOs2nBf\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnut2cLONPNDaqfIX6Px3IXd\">\n<div data-page-id=\"T0IWdoiEeosVc3xKr09c1WHEnQh\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnpSttN1ag64ruA42gX9ji1g\">亲爱的狩月人：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnIRwoKn8n9d3KJFwdW0uElc\">感谢您的关注与支持，以下是华胥资料片「大风歌&middot;上」2025年12月23日版本更新说明，辛苦查阅。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnIRwoKn8n9d3KJFwdW0uElc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnlezWbXSNBDJLQEklBJIznh\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">▍</span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">维护更新说明</span></h3>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcndWGBWorP7tUgjg9NKRlfgc\"><strong>◆维护时间◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnamR5PtkIwUE5TxJMK9efTb\">2025年12月23日（星期二）04:00-11:00（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnqa3LqtSygwH0BA7O4X3frc\">*开服时间视维护进度有可能提前或推迟，还请留意公告通知。维护更新期间所有服务器将无法登录，请狩月人合理安排游戏时间。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnARNb6dfJx4kWgSe1EI586d\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcn4LwH5lcqwqqnmsjn7ipnTS\"><strong>◆维护补偿◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnjT6pEutDbC8x23S7MTrmvf\">月石*300、委托手册&middot;二*6、委托手册&middot;三*4、玩具气锤*10</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn7lws61tuLqoBKIaQL1odVg\">* 领取条件：解锁【邮件】功能，邮件领取有效时间至2025年12月30日23:59（UTC+8）。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnjEcSCDn72ED1FjszffC7ge\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnQo0nt38q8leuKo5yg2OCRh\"><strong>◆更新方式◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnPxrJRADdq7VNZu1WslhJkg\">PC端：重新开启启动器后，点击【更新游戏】，进行更新；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnq4fM8adDFivElz670UVl8e\">安卓端：进入游戏后，根据游戏弹窗提示进行更新；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcneeiKIAF6TBIoGixTMzSoje\">iOS端：前往App Store进行更新。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn2WxucYoFsYSzR1kAUW0Rad\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnabbeXNeTncnb5t7TLporXd\"><strong>◆设备要求◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn0o1YtCX0cTiwUcLmcsRyfg\">为保证游戏的顺利安装与体验，建议狩月人参考以下配置要求：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnkfQQGN50Hadf1SEye6aq7f\"><strong>最低配置</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn2rSEGPJ20THZt6Odif62wV\">Android：系统Android 8及以上、处理器高通骁龙 845/天玑1000以上、运行内存8GB以上、可用存储空间20GB以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnDaBBvPXPuOBA72h2uHTGfb\">iOS：iPhone 12以上型号、系统版本iOS 15.0以上、可用存储空间20G以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnIUOrsKfDYLM8d79BAu2Mwe\">可用存储空间：20GB以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnlTVPzconNTGRSMCOhFVSxh\">PC：系统Windows 10 64bit以上、处理器Intel Core i5(第九代) /AMD Ryzen 5 2600X以上、显卡Geforce GTX1060/AMD Radeon RX 580以上、运行内存16GB以上、可用存储空间40G以上。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnF7OyCpWH9roP5oNBga1ZVg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcncEROVsZtx6jThl2ZW9aZTh\"><strong>推荐配置</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn8m8bOrsYYrfCFCTWJjOo9e\">Android：系统Android 12、处理器高通骁龙 8Gen 1/ 天玑 9000、内存12GB 以上、可用存储空间20GB 以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn2mCHBQ0BUxyQs8a4xTmpah\">iOS：机型iPhone 14 Pro、系统iOS 17.0、可用存储空间20GB及以上；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnh6Dd8IDlUnEqen8jfT7yOd\">PC：系统Windows 10 64bit、处理器:Intel core i7(第十代)/AMD Ryzen 7 3700x、显卡GeForce RTX 2060/AMD Radeon RX5700XT、运行内存32GB及以上、预留硬盘空间：40GB及以上。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnKplIf4wi35XqNfk7cc2Aah\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnTWqn2WWlsNrVBmfFr3Q4eb\"><strong>手柄支持</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn4Umm64cUhgyysASIoxEIlc\">目前《二重螺旋》于PC设备支持以下控制器。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnDaNmAw5yF0AZy5x6hml5Oh\">有线/无线控制器：Xbox系列、Xbox Elite系列；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnSFs21ym0UTF7snF1E6tk9d\">无线控制器：DualSense&reg;、DualSense Edge&trade;；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn8RnvSzUTzEpTLYZfmM1Ctc\">有线控制器：DUALSHOCK&reg;4。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnnXSI47cyElcNoWvE9giB4g\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-3 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnlezWbXSNBDJLQEklBJIznh\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\">▍</span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>版本全新内容&nbsp;</strong></span></h3>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnhW8XHTk5ZBEregVuOZPlPo\"><strong>◆全新剧情任务开放◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnuSe24ceD9IzqFWf3aMVgvE\">「烟津掠影蔽香尘」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnU7bPMYC8lh5tHuIL5PDPnb\">经过一路上的远渡重洋，你终于来到了名为华胥的国度。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcns8E80TLd7LaQ6TnqRqvXDc\">举目望去的秀美风景提醒着你已身处异乡。与止流聊聊，了解华胥的更多信息吧。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnR4sCxuBdxkTtBiUyD0jGyg\">✦ 开放时间：12月23日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnBc4sZ110BHqjWFcTf173Ve\">✦ 开放条件：完成世界纪游剧情【寻物启事】后解锁，历练等级要求42级。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnFZAy0o0jcYfTP5aRn266pd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnUJXX3aKQtFK6HFWmdButLc\">「光阴集&middot;扶疏」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcna5ciLb2zCeTOzENc0kc5Ld\">历经百年沉眠的医师，想为你治疗不眠的症候。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn89MWqyC85ZGkJX6afWDyqd\">✦ 开放时间：12月23日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn95qaWdraSuPOJn2qgwIOVe\">✦ 开放条件：获取角色「扶疏」后，即可于【休憩之所】-【点滴】处查看</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnEAfEFJJ98CXQC3bDL1AHvf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnaXh95sLWTTbGccJmns0sgf\">「光阴集&middot;刻舟」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnxpLI6Fdap7hVMPFAaGCfsf\">但凡树林茂密或是芦苇交横处，总有隐逸的游侠留下的传闻。这些故事恩怨情仇居多。然而真正的出世之人，连一点踪迹也不会留下。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnctgyMLZwehrXBxQ4GI8mze\">✦ 开放时间：1月20日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnkt8HeUwq1HY8mWf6haM7Rg\">✦ 开放条件：获取角色「刻舟」并完成主线任务「初谒华胥」后，即可于【休憩之所】-【点滴】处查看。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnru2nNp3cAmegK0TKbz5EKb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnpvC9wxRd6kVM4sCgK8I0Qb\"><strong>◆全新区域探索开放◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnauMyE19falY3z3xaPK1EAg\">「烟津渡」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnRjhmL8WX2VgfY0Evj1DH3e\">位于华胥南侧入海交汇处的大型渡口区域，临近旧都皓京。气候宜人，风景秀美。承接贸易中转的区域功能，通常作为外国人来到华胥的首要落脚点。</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcntZDL82aBrmeemxDRbsXKqe\"><strong>◆全新角色◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnSSUEwfibatC3oPesx08dWb\">水属性&middot;「扶疏」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnYIbQqmsswZKmV6A4ZswVtf\">✦ 武器精通：鞭刃/弓</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnvMMpt07LA7HGtBVP7DZHff\">✦ 获取开放时间：12月23日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnMnhHZjP2xtKYe8I814d2Fe\">✦ 获取方式：委托密函免费获得/商城购买获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnLA4po7211jRuSJyIpMGtBc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnbx2Ele5UwflPq5gpmXgEdh\">光属性&middot;「刻舟」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcndxfDUIa07TjHjh9yCSVrMe\">✦ 武器精通：全部类型</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnm9yAnIkKd8fnuQmKqqnZeg\">✦ 获取开放时间：1月20日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnmZEjdBizrnMXhUBrtivfBc\">✦ 获取方式：委托密函免费获得/商城购买获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcntEik2txPvri4lcGdPEiUFg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnK7bjp2XAvXD0kpdV9WfVlf\"><strong>◆全新武器◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnmIpCbM6wiUn6aMEn5ex2Ne\">鞭刃&middot;「泽世的慈雨」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnQN92xbebxtpdzUG910FIZg\">✦ 获取方式：通过铸造免费获得/通过商店购买获得；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnfD0xyTUgEUtj2IKqIYoZge\">✦ 获取开放时间：12月23日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnHyp5QSHbteMpqvJjC6pvze\">*「密函：泽世的慈雨」通过当期沉浸式戏剧【观剧纪念】商店购买获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnJFmnOO4WZlX1QsDTx0BQMb\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnQYLteKnPcnkt9iZTirumAd\">突击枪&middot;「雀舞云屏」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGO49s8ORuu1Pk8uuFxVAnh\">✦ 获取方式：通过铸造免费获得/通过商店购买获得；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnbzjeXmHAIMTUoSZ5hHHIvh\">✦ 获取开放时间：12月23日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnNIIVW7Mn3W5AxCGn6WF6qd\">*「密函：雀舞云屏」通过梦魇残声获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnTcUwsJ0Litx91Dq3Pl01Gd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn1godyp6gZn2VuO1aStUPyd\">突击枪&middot;「若华的飞光」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnWi7ErOYcJsPU3NbaTn0a6d\">✦ 获取方式：通过铸造免费获得/通过商店购买获得；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnsldMIwbPnfR5hzKiQoc5jf\">✦ 获取开放时间：1月20日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnSeAIAKEfdUTNq8CXgOHTXc\">*「密函：若华的飞光」通过当期沉浸式戏剧【观剧纪念】商店购买获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn63cGZH1LXndM8IoFJRGrid\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnbVTOjc8aJfCnctMld4qfgd\">长柄&middot;「未来之鸽」</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnERVq141o5k4xCAszKRsF2c\">✦ 获取方式：通过铸造免费获得/通过商店购买获得；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn7KONDg2pxFbpER9Ns3iwUe\">✦ 获取开放时间：1月20日（UTC+8）更新后长期开放；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnv7yLqqYdK9gkLR4PkZ8S1b\">*「密函：未来之鸽」通过梦魇残声获得。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn9W7BPAs4IalKfkGxl8oUId\">&nbsp;</div>\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-doxcnvryTEdhHU3dVdQ9AhihU1b\"><strong>◆全新委托密函轮换说明◆</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnYQ2nCkEbqyPR56B6niytqe\">12月23日更新后（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnz95dWe17YjSa0toUikWGjG\">「密函：扶疏」「密函：泽世的慈雨」将替换「密函：菲娜」「密函：织梦的白羽」加入沉浸式戏剧的限时奖励中；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnHR0UqOjYW1VeE9UbGkXh7b\">「密函：菲娜」将替换「密函：莉兹贝尔」加入梦魇残声；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnRKQlfPrLTOLS487VoInPmd\">「密函：织梦的白羽」将替换「密函：引浪小调」加入梦魇残声；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnugRyUidOEvpcC4EBQ42BSc\">「密函：雀舞云屏」将替换「密函：茵布拉花序」加入梦魇残声；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn4qdURKGKlev2q23zCSehXb\">「密函：莉兹贝尔」「密函：引浪小调」「密函：茵布拉花序」将永久加入【委托密函】商店兑换中。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnGC0WE6aq6Ve6k3aLyhXSlc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnZ7OHaWweGpFCUuS0Y4B2Vb\">1月20日10:00（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnx614uqUqPMGDyvuDQvOLzh\">「密函：刻舟」「密函：若华的飞光」将替换「密函：扶疏」「密函：泽世的慈雨」加入沉浸式戏剧的限时奖励中；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnhBZMFcTu75eNte5gIMKmIb\">「密函：扶疏」将替换「密函：黎瑟」加入梦魇残声；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnWvfkJBseOe3Wpfx3hhnB7b\">「密函：泽世的慈雨」将替换「密函：放逐怒雷」加入梦魇残声；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn8qg5YaAMuwJOYLaShf89Id\">「密函：未来之鸽」将替换「密函：春玦戟」加入梦魇残声；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnpIm3Q6jzED3gECOOpml7Zg\">「密函：黎瑟」「密函：放逐怒雷」「密函：春玦戟」将永久加入【委托密函】商店兑换中。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-recor